data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Beautiful 2-year-old home!  5 Bedrooms and an office. 3 Full Baths, Master features beautiful all tile shower and large walk-in closet, This home checks all the boxes. Luxury Vinyl plank flooring everywhere, 3 CM Quartz countertops in Kitchen and all baths. Larger lot with privacy all around. Backs to woods with plenty of room for your pool. Roof over lani! Open concept with 12 foot ceilings in common area and 9'4" in Bedrooms and Baths. Crown and raised trim. Gutters, Solar powered roof fans, pull down attic stairs, concrete trim everywhere outside outlines windows, and all doors. Quality block construction and extra insulation are just a few of the features this home has vs many others on the market.Owner has spent thousands on a CAT 5 system for your home office needs. You need to put this one on your list!
